Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm back, everyone! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaleido Star is about to start. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's make sure to watch Kaleido Star\Naccording to the usual promise,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have a lot of fun! Fun! Fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I keep on\Nthinking of myself as your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You're not my dream anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:10.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the beginning I was a\Nlittle hyperconscious of you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:17.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't just let go and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:27.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's strange, isn't it?\NI couldn't get you off my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:35.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But our feelings just kept running in parallel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want us to blend together {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:41.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like the coffee and milk in café au lait{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:43.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Slowly and easily {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:51.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Blanc et noir, I'm sure we can) We should be able\Nto have that bitter-and-sweet relationship{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:59.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(We are harmony)\NOui, with you the harmony would be wonderful{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:06.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to play that harmony\Nwith my special person{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're going to\Nstart from where we left off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"People of Our Time:\Nthe Kaleido Stage's New Star,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are we recording the real thing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora Naegino," take five!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was your 200th performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the power of the Angel's\NManeuver that brought you this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Because now the Angel's Maneuver\Nis something we all do together like {\i1}zoom{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is! It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There appear to be some fans who call\Nthe Layla Hamilton days "The Era of Fire"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and these days "The Era of Light."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of those, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of those, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't she do better than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,completest possible honors...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now Sora's second to no one,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}not even Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Angel's Maneuver... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the rest of the cast\Nbecome members of the audience,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the whole audience becomes one being,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and an angel stage is born. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A maneuver that makes the whole stage one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if someday I'll be able to make one too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real one, right? I feel like, "bwaaa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like "eeee!", or "ohhhh," or maybe "kyaaa!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a stage that only I can make.\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new constellation is beginning to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The constellation Aries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking to? Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean Rosetta's\Ngoing to become the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Sora mumbling to herself about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, become the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, what's this about Miss\NRosetta becoming the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is we weren't\Nplanning to announce it yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For this year's Kenneth\NCorporation "Special Show,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we plan to cast Rosetta Passel in a lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be precise she'll\Nbe co-starring with Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it kinda feels like\Nthe moment's finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rosetta, what are your comments\Nabout being chosen for the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll do my best to\Nmeet everyone's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to meet everyone's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Miss Rosetta Passel,\Nexpressing her enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the sudden announcement\Nof the lead role in their new show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really just too sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, is this the script for the new show?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the title is\N"The Princess Without a Smile"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, when Rosetta\Nfirst came here she never smiled, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is it a Diabolo Master princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mia, this isn't written in\Ninvisible ink or anything, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't actually been\Nable to write a single page yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But it's already been announced!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it has...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of have a really vague concept, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just won't come together somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can do it, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Miss Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably in her own room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A catalyst. If I could just find a catalyst...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah, you have a package!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to meet everyone's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should title the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of title?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "Kaleido Star: The Even More\NAmazing Rosetta," or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! That's great, Master Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Master Fool"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how wonderful! It has a great ring to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mask comes off?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess it's not something{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be surprised about...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe it's good that\Nthey get along. Maybe. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! Wait! Miss Sarah, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rip this thing apart! I'll burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll torch it! Torch it! Torch it!\NTorch it! Torch it! Torch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because they messed up your order\Ndoesn't mean you have to treat it like garbage--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this princess and jester?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my money back! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about "princess and jester"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell a catalyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey, Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw this thing in the dumpster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took a big chunk of cash from me,\Nand then they sent me this filthy painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only dirty because it's old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she kind of look like Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! She really does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Rosetta would look\Nlike this if she were a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Ken, are you in love with Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more person in that painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, behind the curtain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be the jester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fool... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This jester fascinates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm going to dispose of this painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me that picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now announce the title of our next show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "The Princess and the Fool."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, "fool" refers\Nto the court jesters of old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're what would now be called "clowns."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess, who has\Nshut her heart to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in love with a jester she saw as\Na child, who exists in her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story is that the one who opens the\Ndoors to her heart isn't one of her court jesters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a prince who loves her\Nfrom the bottom of his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but can't even do a single juggling trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be three teams of jesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll divide up the cast later,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the team leaders are\Nthese three: Anna, Leon, and May.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised Mr. Leon\Naccepted the role of a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll be able to get any laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in this show we'll have a special guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a team of special guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Jonathan and I look\Nforward to working with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new performer arrives on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This show was written with the\Nobject of making Rosetta a lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the director, Mia, wrote\Nit with a specific inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I based it on this painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell on the computer screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this painting has the\Npower to draw people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please look at this painting\Nwith your own eyes at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mood of the entire stage\Nis very important to this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere of the era the\Nprince and the princess lived in,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the feelings of the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you sense those\Nthings from this painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use that image to build your characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The success of this show
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rests on each individual's preparation\Nand visualization of their character.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then! Mass\Nrehearsals start in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody keep in mind what\NMia just said, and get into character.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:10:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All good to the right! All good to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nightly turning on of lights, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stage Training in Progress.\NDo Not Disturb. Sora and Rosetta"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, please return my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get my smile back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even juggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why today I've called\Nthree fools here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, make the princess smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm the first fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm standing in for the other two too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, come on! A little cooperation here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get the point of Fool playing a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can play the prince another time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! You always say "next time,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never get to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just break off this practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?! You're trifling with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't actually have lines
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the real thing, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mia went to the trouble of writing lines
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because she said they'd make\Nit easier to build the characters--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly true that it's better to build\Na character physically than by saying lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get started.\NI'll teach you step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, to begin with let's adjourn to the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that overdoing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually I might not\Nhave thrown him hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Rosetta, about practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rehearsals start in three days, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for me to study\Nthis character and put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This story is about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me from back when I was\Ncalled the Diabolo Machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I know everything about this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Sora,\Nteach me the trampoline!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I want to jump! Much, much higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're back alre--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you like, the Legendary\NGreat Maneuver or the Angel's Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his mask is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get back your smile no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am, then you're a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would give even my life for your smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool. Fool? Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! You demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were kind of mumbling to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About "angels" and "demons"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?\NThe animal costumes are good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my move--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I'm sorry! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... really might be a tough role...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's pretty funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia's a genius for\Ndeciding to cast Leon as a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... From the beginning again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just do the part where\Nthe princess smiles at the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this girl better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's wrong, Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this character according to\Nmy own understanding, just like you told--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think your performance is off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said this princess was you from back\Nwhen you were called the Diabolo Machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the smile you got back\Nfrom doing the Diabolo Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was really lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your smile in performance\Njust now looked pained somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's do it again, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you just don't want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the lead, but you only get to\Nperform for a few minutes at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the rest of the time you're just\Nwatching the clowns do their thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's more, in your big moment\Nto shine all you get to do is smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the way you're thinking about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,quit your role right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, Rosetta's doing her best...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Rosetta's partner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good is it if {\i1}you {\i0}go easy on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be careless,\Ngo at her with all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being careless about my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't think I'm going easy on her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Rosetta gets\Nhow important this role is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's feeling the pressure {\i1}because {\i0}she gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She took on the lead role,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's different than she thought it would\Nbe and she can't work up any confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she probably wants to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although {\i1}you {\i0}probably\Nwouldn't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, I get that as\Nmuch as the next person--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "pressure" isn't in your dictionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't the kind of thing\Nthat training will make any better...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we've just got to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't get it. What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, which one of these three lovely\Nladies is the one who's not wearing a bra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your prize is riding on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Fool, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, what's wrong? I see sweat--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fool, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Layla Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while! Um, are you busy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cathy said she wanted to revise the script,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're not performing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Rosetta's the lead this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makkoli is doing her best\Nto prepare for her debut too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, can I stop here for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous. You have\N20 more to do today. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it seems like you're
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you think you'll\Nbe able to come to the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good. Okay then, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's no good,\NI shouldn't lean on Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken said he saw you come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you noticed too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jester looks exactly like Fool, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the princess looks like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure makes you curious\Nabout their relationship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing, so it must be winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess maybe he's trying\Nto entertain the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see Fool anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard I was chosen by the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "Now I can be with Sora."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And with Miss Layla too."\NI thought, "I'm next."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my dream is hopeless now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my dream to do a\Nlegendary great maneuver with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rosetta! Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Oh, I want to give you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ this home cooking filled with love! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's brought you a box dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special Chinese dinner\Nthat can rid you of all your cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! We have to ask the\Npolice to search for her right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my dad get the car for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My theory is that she's gone to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that's what she did last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? What should\NI do? Oh, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we make it on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We think she got on a plane to Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute; you must remember her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, but the last plane to\NParis took off two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means she's not on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about when\NI brought her back to the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan says to leave this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Wai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. When am I finally\Ngoing to get to the airport?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single cab will stop\Nbecause they all think I'm a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of dust and cobwebs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way do I want to\Ncamp out here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fool's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try to master this\Nmaneuver, for the sake of your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish... is your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two people who, although they\Nwished for each other's smiles,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were never allowed to smile at each other...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Memories he'd sealed away\Nin order to hide his sadness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And all kinds of feelings he's watched\Nplay out as the Spirit of the Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora's, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May's... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My feelings... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why was I trying to run away? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I can't see Fool\Nanymore, I still love the stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to perform on the\Nstage that gave me my smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and give lots of other people smiles too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd started to forget that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, she's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made us worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you Jonathan had a good nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as good as a police dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? You're coming back\Nto the stage, right Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the only\None who can play that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I almost forgot something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever lose sight of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to try to be a true star!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta Passel, who has\Nbeen chosen by the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my name is Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Spirit of the Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the many wishes and feelings and\Ndreams that have been poured into the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must all be here in every age.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, let's do this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Kaleido Stage full of smiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made by true stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I spaced out for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's opening day! Get a grip, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, ten seconds to curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:23:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gather around, o ye fools! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the Kaleido Stage. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.56,0:24:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good fortune go to those\Nwith wings in their hearts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.27,0:24:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
